  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[DigiXros -2] 5 Digimon cards w/different names + [Dragon],
    [saur], or [Ceratopsian] in one of its traitsOn play, place from hand/battle
    area under this card. Reduce play cost per card.\uFF1CRush\uFF1E (This Digimon
    may attack the turn it was played.)[On Play] Delete 1 of your opponent's Digimon
    with 3000 or less. For each card with [Dragon], [saur] or [Ceratopsian] in one
    of its traits in this Digimon's digivolution cards, add 2000 DP to the maximum
    DP you can choose with this effect."
